      section#c-Pullquote
        h2 The #[code .c-Pullquote] Component
        p.
          A #[code .c-Pullquote] tends to have a stronger effect than generic #[code blockquote] Elements.
          Use it when the original source is less than 40 words and contains no paragraph breaks.
          Do not include child #[code p] Elements. To cite the source, add a child
          #[code .c-Pullquote__Src] Component.
        figure
          blockquote.c-Pullquote(cite="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1648163/quotes").
            Look at you, soaring through the air like an eagle&hellip; piloting a blimp.
            #[cite.c-Pullquote__Src: abbr(title="Genetic Lifeform and Disk Operating System") GLaDOS]
      section#c-ListAction
        h2 The #[code .c-ListAction] Component
